			input#cross-sitescripting.b-article__checkbox(type='checkbox', tabindex='1')
			label(for='cross-sitescripting') Межсайтовый скриптинг
			a.sub-list-marker [+]
			ul.sub-list
				li
					a(href='https://www.owasp.org/index.php/XSS_(Cross_Site_Scripting)_Prevention_Cheat_Sheet') XSS cheat sheet
